Package org.gbif.checklistbank.ws.client.guice

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChecklistBankWsClientModule
    A complete guice module that exposes the full ChecklistBank API or a configurable subset.
    ChecklistBankWsMatchClientModule
    Guice module that includes an implementation for the ChecklistBank NameUsageMatchingService.
    ChecklistBankWsSearchClientModule
    Guice module that includes an implementation for the ChecklistBank NameUsageSearchService.
    ChecklistBankWsServiceClientModule
    Guice module that includes implementations for all the ChecklistBank services apart from NameUsageSearchService.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    ChecklistBankSearchWs
    Guice binding annotation.
    ChecklistBankWs
    Guice binding annotation intended to be applied to injected parameters specific to NameUsageWsClient.
    NameUsageMatchWs
    Guice binding annotation intended to be applied to injected parameters specifying the URL of the nub lookup service.
